nd users.<br />\nSince this is not the first time things were broken I&#8217;ve decided to discontinue the thing entirely.</p>\n<h3>Why kill it now?</h3>\n<p>Because having an affiliate program didn&#8217;t bring the increased sales I&#8217;d hope for. It added nothing to anyones experience, for AdRotate or it&#8217;s &#8216;ecosystem&#8217;. With the added thing of signups being broken there really was no point in keeping it around.<br />\nI thought it would bring a sense of community with as extra benefit that people could earn some money by promoting AdRotate Pro for me. But it didn&#8217;t really pan out that way, unfortunately.</p>\n<h3>Thanks</h3>\n<p>Thanks for all who joined and sent many people to adrotateplugin.com. Over the past 8 months several thousand people have been gone through your links.<br />\nReferrals have been paid earlier this week (as per the normal schedule) currently outstanding referrals will be paid in the next few days. </p>\n<p>So effective immediately the affiliate program has been discontinued.<br />\nI don&#8217;t think it will return &#8211; Not anytime soon anyway.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2014/04/effective-immediately-affiliate-program-discontinued/\">Effective Immediately &#8211; Affiliate Program discontinued</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.adrotateplugin.com\">AdRotate for WordPress</a>.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~4/RaJNPfl68gI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2014/04/effective-immediately-affiliate-program-discontinued/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/mod